quote.summary: Beijing UBOX Online Technology Corp is a China-based company mainly engaged in smart retail business. The Company operates in five segments. Unmanned Retail Business Segment mainly retails fast-moving consumer goods such as food and beverages through vending machines. Advertising and System Support Services segment mainly includes display screen advertising services, after-payment advertising services, merchandise display advertising services and machine body advertising services. Merchandise Wholesale segment mainly offers merchandise wholesale to the customers. Vending Machine Sales and Leases segment consist of vending machine sales and leases and provision of hardware support services. Others segment includes mobile device distribution services, karaoke booth services, karaoke booth sales and leases and karaoke booth operation system support.
